name: seeded_apps_tabs
label: Seeded App Tabs
description: App level tabs to be shown to the user for seeded apps. Set to ['*'] by default, denoting all tabs visible. To enable tabs of your choice, replace * and add text as mentioned, to the array: GENERAL,MENU,SECURITY,WORKFLOW,PROPERTY,PROCESSOR,HEALTHCHECK,NLP,CONFIG,SCHEDULER,ASYNCTASKSCHECK
